Titolo: Echo Night 2: The Lord of Nightmares

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Echo Night 2: Nemuri no Shihaisha is a 1999 first-person adventure video game developed and published by FromSoftware for the PlayStation. It is the second game in the Echo Night series, but has an independent story unrelated to the original Echo Night. A fan translation was released in 2015, translating its title as Echo Night 2: The Lord of Nightmares.